      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable and stylish ride? This car is in great shape and has been well-cared for, making it a fantastic choice for your next vehicle! It drives smoothly and looks wonderful, showing only the minor signs of use you'd expect from a well-loved car. It's ready for many more miles of adventure with its next owner!",
