    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age in several areas. The engine runs consistently but may require a tune-up in the near future, and the exterior has some noticeable scratches and minor dings from regular use. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and wear on the driver's seat. It's a solid, functional car for someone looking for affordable transportation without the frills of a newer model.",
