    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and reliably, with all major systems functioning as expected. The exterior is in good shape overall, though you will find some minor door dings and light surface scratches consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. It\u2019s a solid, dependable car that offers a great balance of performance and value for its next owner.",
      "price": 33500.0,
