    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of uncompromising quality and peerless preservation. This unit remains in showroom condition, exhibiting a standard of care that ensures its status as a premier example of the marque. From the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, every detail has been meticulously maintained to meet the expectations of the most discerning buyer. An investment-grade acquisition for those who demand excellence.",
      "price": 46500.0,
